cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about object detection using a deep learning model with deformable parts. The most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with image analysis and object detection. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of convolutional neural networks, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category.
